A few hundred students from the universities of Isfahan created a human shield on Tuesday around the Isfahan nuclear technology center where uranium is processed.
They thus openly expressed that they would defend their country's nuclear program at the risk of their own lives.
The International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) noted in its latest report that Iran has continued to strengthen its nuclear weapons.
